result.name: Centre de Vin

reviews.text: My pork rack was COLD and dry and they gave me a horrible mug for coffee instead of normal tea cup and saucer. It was shocking.

CENTRE DE VIN is an amazing new Oenological Centre where one can find any kind of wine and spirituous in Hong-Kong!
From French wine, Japanese Sake, Whisky from Scotland, Australian, Georgian or Chilean wines... and more! Come and visit to discover by yourself this new wine lovers paradise. 
The Centre includes a huge shop made of wonderful wooden structure proposing an outstanding choice of wines, spirituous & champaigns (the famous Du Moustier), a wine tasting conference room, an italian restaurant, a pool billard, some private rooms for your events, on a weekly basis you can join the happy hour wine tasting... but many other events take place in CENTRE DE VIN. Come and check, Shirley will advise you perfectly!
It is the perfect place to come after a long day of work to relax with a glass of wine, for a delicious dinner or to meet new people.
Only 3 minutes walk from Ngau Tau Kok MTR Station, Exit A.
Enjoy the wine!
Great lunch with salad bar
Nice collection of wine
野食是大家樂feel, 不是法國菜，酒的質素都好差， 似係存放不專業。 一句講哂， 垃圾！

result.name: 維港葡萄酒中心

reviews.text: 野食是大家樂feel, 不是法國菜，酒的質素都好差， 似係存放不專業。 一句講哂， 垃圾！
午餐豬鞍吾錯，不過最吾好系個沙律吧，硬性規定要食之餘，仲要"渣"

#紅菜頭沙律 第一次食紅菜頭，不是我杯茶🙈🙈
#蘑菇忌廉湯 如果冇咁稀就好🙈🙈
#麵包 好好味～加埋油醋，正👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻
#士多啤梨紅酒燴羊膝伴薯菜 好大隻，味道都ok😊😊
#歡樂樹頭蛋糕 個人唔太喜歡cream cake,,呢個都唔錯，但食到最後會覺得好「漏」🙈🙈
#咖啡 苦味好重
今午參與過百的私人包場活動，食物不錯，服務一流。
lunch 的食物等左45分鐘先有，味道普通，一定不會再去
